# pre-push commands to run prior to any branches/commits being pushed up:
# - `npm run build`              - Build the codebase to lib/ so that all configuration files are up-to-date.
# - `npm run check`              - Run the validation checks on the entire codebase.
# - `npm run test.unit.coverage` - Ensure unit tests pass and test coverage is valid.
